"```sql\nSELECT c.Text\nFROM comments c\nJOIN posts p ON c.PostId = p.Id\nWHERE p.Title LIKE '%linear regression%';\n```\n\nThis SQL query selects the `Text` of comments from the `comments` table that are associated with posts in the `posts` table where the `Title` contains the phrase \"linear regression\". The join is performed using the foreign key relationship between `comments.PostId` and `posts.Id`."